[2014-03-11 16:06:33] - MySql AppModel.class.php (110) - SELECT servus_products.*,
                c1.name as category,
                c2.name as subcategory,
                servus_product_lines.name as product_line,
                servus_product_images.name as listing_image,
                servus_href.ref as ref,
                h1.ref as category_ref,
                h2.ref as subcategory_ref
            FROM servus_products
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_product_categories c1
                ON servus_products.product_category_id = c1.id
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_product_categories c2
                ON servus_products.product_subcategory_id = c2.id
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_product_lines
                ON servus_products.line_id = servus_product_lines.id
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_product_images
                ON servus_product_images.product_id = servus_products.id AND servus_product_images.type = 'listing'
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_href
                ON servus_href.content_id = servus_products.id and servus_href.type = 'product'
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_href h1
                ON h1.content_id = servus_products.product_category_id and h1.type = 'product_category'
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_href h2
                ON h2.content_id = servus_products.product_subcategory_id and h2.type = 'product_category'
             GROUP BY servus_products.id ORDER BY id DESC

[2014-03-11 19:08:00] - MySql AppModel.class.php (60) - SELECT servus_pages.*,
                servus_users.first_name as author,
                p.title as parent_page,
                servus_href.ref
            FROM servus_pages
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_pages p
                ON p.id = servus_pages.parent
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_users
                ON servus_pages.user_id = servus_users.id
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_href
                ON servus_pages.id = servus_href.content_id AND servus_href.type = 'page'
            WHERE servus_pages.id = 44

                servus_users.first_name as author,
                p.title as parent_page,
                servus_href.ref
            FROM servus_pages
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_pages p
                ON p.id = servus_pages.parent
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_users
                ON servus_pages.user_id = servus_users.id
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_href
                ON servus_pages.id = servus_href.content_id AND servus_href.type = 'page'
            WHERE servus_pages.id = 77

[2014-03-11 19:39:41] - MySql AppModel.class.php (60) - SELECT servus_pages.*,
                servus_users.first_name as author,
                p.title as parent_page,
                servus_href.ref
            FROM servus_pages
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_pages p
                ON p.id = servus_pages.parent
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_users
                ON servus_pages.user_id = servus_users.id
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_href
                ON servus_pages.id = servus_href.content_id AND servus_href.type = 'page'
            WHERE servus_pages.id = 44

[2014-03-11 19:53:15] - MySql AppModel.class.php (60) - SELECT servus_pages.*,
                servus_users.first_name as author,
                p.title as parent_page,
                servus_href.ref
            FROM servus_pages
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_pages p
                ON p.id = servus_pages.parent
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_users
                ON servus_pages.user_id = servus_users.id
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_href
                ON servus_pages.id = servus_href.content_id AND servus_href.type = 'page'
            WHERE servus_pages.id = 77

            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_users
                ON servus_pages.user_id = servus_users.id
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_href
                ON servus_pages.id = servus_href.content_id AND servus_href.type = 'page'
            WHERE servus_pages.id = 16

                servus_users.first_name as author,
                p.title as parent_page,
                servus_href.ref
            FROM servus_pages
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_pages p
                ON p.id = servus_pages.parent
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_users
                ON servus_pages.user_id = servus_users.id
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_href
                ON servus_pages.id = servus_href.content_id AND servus_href.type = 'page'
            WHERE servus_pages.id = 44

                p.title as parent_page,
                servus_href.ref
            FROM servus_pages
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_pages p
                ON p.id = servus_pages.parent
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_users
                ON servus_pages.user_id = servus_users.id
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_href
                ON servus_pages.id = servus_href.content_id AND servus_href.type = 'page'
            WHERE servus_pages.id = 77

                servus_users.first_name as author,
                p.title as parent_page,
                servus_href.ref
            FROM servus_pages
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_pages p

            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_users
                ON servus_pages.user_id = servus_users.id
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_href
                ON servus_pages.id = servus_href.content_id AND servus_href.type = 'page'
            WHERE servus_pages.id = 44

            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_users
                ON servus_pages.user_id = servus_users.id
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_href
                ON servus_pages.id = servus_href.content_id AND servus_href.type = 'page'
            WHERE servus_pages.id = 16

            WHERE servus_pages.status = '1' AND servus_pages.parent = '0' AND servus_pages.id <> '16' ORDER BY title ASC

                servus_href.ref
            FROM servus_pages
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_pages p
                ON p.id = servus_pages.parent
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_users
                ON servus_pages.user_id = servus_users.id
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_href
                ON servus_pages.id = servus_href.content_id AND servus_href.type = 'page'
            WHERE servus_pages.id = 16

[2014-03-11 21:49:32] - MySql AppModel.class.php (110) - SELECT servus_products.*,

                h2.ref as subcategory_ref
            FROM servus_products
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_product_categories c1
                ON servus_products.product_category_id = c1.id
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_product_categories c2
                ON servus_products.product_subcategory_id = c2.id
            LEFT OUTER JOIN servus_product_lines
                ON servus_products.line_id = servus_product_lines.id

                ON servus_product_images.product_id = servus_products.id AND servus_product_images.type = 'listing'

            WHERE servus_products.status = '1' AND servus_products.product_category_id = '4' GROUP BY servus_products.id ORDER BY display_order ASC
